profile: Kriger Contracting is a veteran owned and operated residential general contracting business, proudly servicing the Fraser Valley, offering quality contracting services, based on the values and skills acquired form over 9 years of service in the Canadian Armed Forces. Kriger Contracting bases its business practices off the experiences and values learned from the military; Service, Integrity, Stewardship, and Excellence.
